## ⚙️ How It Works
1. **Data Collection** — Twitter dataset loaded (CSV format)
2. **Text Preprocessing** — Cleaning tweets:
   - Removing URLs, mentions, hashtags
   - Lowercasing
   - Removing stopwords
   - Tokenization
   - Stemming / Lemmatization
3. **Feature Extraction** — Text Vectorization using TF-IDF
4. **Model Training** — Trained using classification algorithms
5. **Evaluation** — Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1-Score
6. **Prediction** — Predicts sentiment of new tweets
